text:
Hi everyone. 

I don't know if this is the right channel to post this but I want to post details about an upcoming tech event called DIVERSITECH FEST.

It's all about networking. 

Networking can get you into doors that degrees cannot. It's time to break out and get a job in tech or at least know where to start in tech. 

Come network and connect with Tech recruiters, Tech Founders, Tech Investors etc at the Diversitech Fest coming up from May 10th -12th, 2022 organized by Tribaja and have fun while doing it. 

There will be networking like crazy virtually. 

The Fest is dedicated to Art, Music, Culture, Technology and lnnovation. 

Tribaja is a brand that connects tech talents to companies with vision. 

They also help with resources and trainings to enhance tech careers, tech transition etc. 

The Diversitech Fest is aimed at making people understand how people of diversity can succeed in the tech industry despite the lack of resources. 

This event will help connect diverse techies to tech companies, which will aid in building relationships between them. 

Come join the event let Tribaja be a part of your tech journey, get your free tickets to attend the event :point_right: <http://www.eventbrite.com/e/307500621637/?discount=Ene%40DiversitechFest|here>!

attachments.text: Diversitech Fest is the East Coast's largest conference dedicated to art, music, culture, technology, and innovation.
